Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/archiver/?tid-24466660.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Farchiver%2F%3Ftid-24466660.html&d=YSHITbnYt1wySyIpTo9jGf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d4aac355\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk/archiver/?tid-24466660.html</a><br />\n總結<br />\n這文章不是堅持馬太福音原文一定是希臘文，這文章是列出部份理據，指出馬太福音原文是希臘文是比較合理。<br />\n<br />\n雖然傳統相信馬太福音原文是希伯來文/亞蘭文，但現代學者從福音書的內容來看，馬太福音原文應該是希臘文。現代學者的研究，不是完全否定所有基督教的傳統，而是重新審視它們，使我們更明白自已的宗教典籍。"},{"pid":"012a003a4342ccedc62a9d23d44b6e6ed113eff0","tid":802081,"uid":111081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cd9462de7e262635aebd16c10fcde1485704bc6","tid":802081,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d670a36abfd38ba892d9d0d8cc57fd841f74e83b","tid":802081,"uid":111081,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"65e7619366c553c7826ea6f6985a1770cb5ab4db","tid":802081,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"西方文化根本冇孝順呢個概念，英文裡面只搵到filial piety一詞，但唔常用，好多西人都唔知點解。<br />\n<br />\n香港啲耶教人士話基督教都重視孝道，十誡第四誡就叫人孝敬父母，但我睇明明係honour your parents，點解譯成孝？完全唔同意思。成本聖經亦無filial piety。耶教徒成日偷換概念，欺哄世人，到底想點？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:38:21.000Z","msg":"但聖經唔係英譯中wor，十誡原文應該係希伯來文。英文無孝順，自然就唯有被譯做honour your parents，唔代表原文唔係孝順既意思。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"情況好似英譯《心經》有版本係根據中文翻譯，和合本就係按英文譯。<br />\n<br />\n另外，希伯來人唔似有「孝」呢個概念，佢哋冇姓氏，耶穌駁嘴同自尋短見都屬不孝。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:06:41.000Z","msg":"Lum深一層，中文好似無詞語翻譯到honour呢個字。<br />\n唉所以中國人先無honour呢個概念/ 想法"},{"pid":"a4ba0316b5a0bcfc7b0b6cb026d7b181855ebbed","tid":802081,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecf715a9ea8c6c74d315b1da6f7b3f9c857dfd44","tid":802081,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5a67fd8cccdd9dd898208a6ef31559a1a2e9268","tid":802081,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4001274229cec648b7a7118212ce0cd4fcdac4","tid":802081,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"講緊傳統西方"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"聖經喺邊度嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"新約除咗馬太福音（亞蘭文寫成），其餘都係希臘文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"希臘文化係咪你講嘅西方文化呀<br />\n有無睇過我的大嚿婚禮?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17503dd94305f4bd28d3e9b7a13f2d06c4062777","tid":802081,"uid":20867,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"75962c3a7ab9969be88f3241bacd2a789c5efbf7","tid":802081,"uid":22719,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港聖經一向鳩譯</blockquote><br />\n我用Linux"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"Windows = IT界聖經<br />\nLinux = IT界異端<br />\n<br />\nTVB = 香港人聖經<br />\nATV = 香港人異端"},{"pid":"49fdf094b0b296f9354cacecd78b6d4593c03cd5","tid":802081,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73458167e9b70eee91d228d34abda10d6c344b38","tid":802081,"uid":193893,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:41:49.000Z","msg":"Honour your parent<br />\n<br />\n立身行道，以顯父母，孝之終也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n翻譯聖經個陣，係一套全新既外來觀念引入中國既時期，有必要迎合本地既固有語言習慣的。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:11:49.000Z","msg":"所以聖經只不過系 marketing/PR 產物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8d29448c0028e28decdd277e91ba93dfad1b42","tid":802081,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25848f1d8da77a80f17b5ac1b4df29dad2387645","tid":802081,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n<br />\n聖經呢d垃圾隨時可以改<br />\n<br />\n迎合到當時嘅蠢人就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n根本當宗教係歷史噉睇（研究點解啲人有咁嘅文化），研究點解會有宗教紛爭，研究社會學同政治就算<br />\n真係去諗人地譯得啱唔啱都嘥氣，一定係唔啱，現代人睇其實宗教只係集體創作，一定有人諗法唔同，當時睇咪就係人地唔同意你就話人00後、child登、炒車、屈毛等，關sir就係神父，有咩好理會啫。"},{"pid":"1339a1417af55b89b1962e490d7bfc58b2890b7f","tid":802081,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:30:47.000Z","msg":"直接訪問外國人俾唔俾家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kKY23R3awB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkKY23R3awB0&d=YSHITbnYt1wySyIpTo9jGf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=82cdc28e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kKY23R3awB0</a>"},{"pid":"81a5a6f65a964a7ad06ff8bf5821417488e4c152","tid":802081,"uid":163662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"咁多位咁打誤會晒，睇完以下經文或者你會好驚奇。<br />\n<br />\n哥林多後書12章14節：兒女不該為父母積財，父母該為兒女積財。<br />\n<br />\n聖經主張父母比返錢仔女，孝順父母意思係要服從父母，接受父母管教，其實好合理，唔通聖經叫d 仔女反父母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0851e7210799fd6bedb25308bd5a953a44256ddf","tid":802081,"uid":163662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"81a5a6f65a964a7ad06ff8bf5821417488e4c152","tid":802081,"uid":163662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"咁多位咁打誤會晒，睇完以下經文或者你會好驚奇。<br />\n<br />\n哥林多後書12章14節：兒女不該為父母積財，父母該為兒女積財。<br />\n<br />\n聖經主張父母比返錢仔女，孝順父母意思係要服從父母，接受父母管教，其實好合理，唔通聖經叫d 仔女反父母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打誤會晒，睇完以下經文或者你會好驚奇。<br />\n<br />\n哥林多後書12章14節：兒女不該為父母積財，父母該為兒女積財。<br />\n<br />\n聖經主張父母比返錢仔女，孝順父母意思係要服從父母，接受父母管教，其實好合理，唔通聖經叫d 仔女反父母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88e44c55485de54c47c35232f31f8c8e5f6c686","tid":802081,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:13:30.000Z","msg":"馬太福音10:34-38<br />\n<br />\n「你們不要想我來是叫地上太平；我來並不是叫地上太平，乃是叫地上動刀兵。<br />\n因為我來是叫人與父親生疏，女兒與母親生疏，媳婦與婆婆生疏。<br />\n人的仇敵就是自己家裡的人。<br />\n愛父母過於愛我的，不配作我的門徒；愛兒女過於愛我的，不配作我的門徒；<br />\n不背著他的十字架跟從我的，也不配作我的門徒。」"},{"pid":"6ad55bb99efbd700d963514c36158288db56cff2","tid":802081,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49fdf094b0b296f9354cacecd78b6d4593c03cd5","tid":802081,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73458167e9b70eee91d228d34abda10d6c344b38","tid":802081,"uid":193893,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:41:49.000Z","msg":"Honour your parent<br />\n<br />\n立身行道，以顯父母，孝之終也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n翻譯聖經個陣，係一套全新既外來觀念引入中國既時期，有必要迎合本地既固有語言習慣的。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:11:49.000Z","msg":"所以聖經只不過系 marketing/PR 產物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"傳教，當然要講marketing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過正如#25咁話，冇一個直接既動詞翻譯honour，所以用立身行道以顯父母呢個孝道既觀念黎翻譯，我認為都係幾準確的做法。<br />\n<br />\n好多時我地睇譯本唔好，未必係英文唔得，而係對中文既掌握或者理解同翻譯家唔一樣。"},{"pid":"d296b61aa5ae724c81670844afafc8966247deef","tid":802081,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ad55bb99efbd700d963514c36158288db56cff2","tid":802081,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49fdf094b0b296f9354cacecd78b6d4593c03cd5","tid":802081,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73458167e9b70eee91d228d34abda10d6c344b38","tid":802081,"uid":193893,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:41:49.000Z","msg":"Honour your parent<br />\n<br />\n立身行道，以顯父母，孝之終也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n翻譯聖經個陣，係一套全新既外來觀念引入中國既時期，有必要迎合本地既固有語言習慣的。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:11:49.000Z","msg":"所以聖經只不過系 marketing/PR 產物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"傳教，當然要講marketing<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma